#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:14
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"These quick action buttons are here to aid you in updating the contact "
"record faster and keep a count of how many times each action has be done."
msgstr ""
"Deze snelle actie knoppen zijn er om je te helpen het contact bestand "
"sneller te updaten en om bij te houden hoevaak een actie uitgevoerd is."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:15
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"For example, If you click the 'No Answer' button 4 times, we will log that "
"you attempted to reach this contact 4 times, but they did not answer. This "
"action will also change the 'Seeker Path' to 'Contact Attempted'."
msgstr ""
"Bijvoorbeeld, als u de 'Geen antwoord' knop 4 keer klikt, registreren we dat "
"u dit contact 4 keer hebt geprobeerd te bereiken, maar dat ze niet hebben "
"geantwoord. Deze actie zal ook het 'Zoekerspad' veranderen naar 'Contact "
"geprobeerd'."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:27
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "User workload status icons legend:"
msgstr "Gebruiikers werklading status icoon legenda:"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:33
msgid "2 contacts need an update"
msgstr "2 contacten hebben een update nodig"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:42
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "This is where you can record notes from meetings and conversations."
msgstr "Dit is waar je notities kan plaatsen van bijeenkomsten en gesprekken."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:43
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"Type @ and the name of a user to mention them in a comment. This user will "
"then receive a notification."
msgstr ""
"Typ @ en de naam van een gebruiker om hen te noemen in een opmerking. Deze "
"gebruiker krijgt hier dan een bericht van."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:44
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"This section also includes the history of activity, such as when the contact "
"or group status became active etc."
msgstr ""
"Deze sectie omvat ook de geschiedenis van de activiteit, zoals wanneer het "
"contact of the groepstatus actief werd enz."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:45
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "You can filter this section either by 'All', 'Comments', or 'Activity'."
msgstr ""
"Je kunt deze sectie filteren d.m.v. \"alles\", \"opmerkingen\" of "
"\"Activiteiten\"."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:58 template-settings.php:118
msgid "Your Profile"
msgstr "Jouw Profiel"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:59
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "In this area you can see your user profile."
msgstr "In dit gedeelte kun je je gebruikers profiel zien."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:60
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"You are not required to fill out any of these profile fields. They are "
"optional to meet your team’s needs."
msgstr ""
"Het invullen van deze velden is niet verplicht. Ze zijn optioneel "
"afhankelijk van de behoeften van je team."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:61
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"By clicking 'Edit', you will be able adjust things like the language that "
"this system operates in."
msgstr ""
"Door op \"Wijzigen\" te klikken, kun je instellinge aanpassen zoals de taal "
"waarin dit systeem opereert."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:66 dt-posts/custom-post-type.php:247
#: dt-users/users.php:169
msgid "Locations"
msgstr "locaties"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:67
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"These are the areas you are responsible for. Clicking the 'Add' button will "
"bring up a list of locations to choose from."
msgstr ""
"Dit zijn de gebieden waar je verantwoordelijk voor bent. Door de \"voeg "
"toe\" knop te klikken komt er een lijst tevoorschijn met locaties waaruit je "
"kunt kiezen."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:72
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "Your Notifications"
msgstr "meldingen"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:73
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"You will receive web notifications and email notifications based on your "
"notification preferences. To change your preference, click the toggle "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"Je ontvangt Web- en e-mail notificaties gebaseerd op je notificatie "
"voorkeuren. Om je voorkeuren aan te passen, klik op de tuimel knoppen."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:75
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "Notifications Turned On: The toggle will appear blue."
msgstr "Notificaties Aan: de tuimelknop is blauw."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:76
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "Notifications Turned Off: The toggle will appear grey."
msgstr "Notificaties Uit: de tuimelknop is grijs."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:78
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"Some of the types of notifications cannot be adjusted because they are "
"required by the system."
msgstr ""
"Sommige type notificaties kunnen niet aangepast worden omdat ze vereist zijn "
"voor het systeem."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:79
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"Adjust whether you want to see notifications about new comments, contact "
"information changes, Contact Milestones and Group Health metrics, and "
"whether to you will receive a notification for any update that happens in "
"the system."
msgstr ""
"Pas aan of je notificaties wilt krijgen over nieuwe opmerkingen, Contact "
"informatie wijzigingen, Contact Mijlpalen en Groep Gezondheids statistieken "
"en of je notificaties wilt ontvangen voor elke update die gemaakt wordt in "
"het systeem."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:87
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "Notifications Page"
msgstr "meldingen"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:88
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"This Notifications Page is where you can read updates to users and groups. "
"It displays notifications about activity on your records."
msgstr ""
"Deze Notificatie Pagina is waar je updates kunt lezen van gebruikers en "
"groepen. Het toont notificaties van activiteiten in jouw bestanden."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:89
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "All / Unread"
msgstr "Alles/ Ongelezen"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:90
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"Click the 'All' button to show the full list of all of your notifications."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de \"Alles\" knop om de volledige lijst van al je notificaties te "
"tonen."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:91
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"Click the 'Unread' button to show the list of all of your unread "
"notifications."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de \"ongelezen\" knop om de lijst te tonen van al je ongelezen "
"notificaties."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:92 dt-assets/parts/nav-topbar.php:332
#: template-notifications.php:66
msgid "Mark all as read"
msgstr "Markeer als Gelezen"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:93
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"If you don't want to click each filled in circle on the right side of each "
"row to indicate the notification has been read, then click the 'Mark All as "
"Read' link at the top to quickly adjust all the messages that they have all "
"been read."
msgstr ""
"Als je niet elk gevulde cirkeltje aan de rechter kant van elke rij wilt "
"aanklikken om aan te geven dat de notificatie gelezen is, klik dan op "
"\"Markeer alles als Gelezen\" link bovenaan om snel aan te geven dat alle "
"berichten gelezen zijn."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:95
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"Click the 'Settings' link to go to the notifications settings area to adjust "
"whether you want to see notifications about new comments, contact "
"information changes, Contact Milestones and Group Health metrics, and "
"whether to you will receive a notification for any update that happens in "
"the system."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de \"instellingen\" link om naar de notificatie instellingen te gaan "
"om aan te passen of je notificaties wilt zien van nieuwe opmerkingen, "
"Contact informatie veranderingen, Contact mijlpalen en Groep Gezondheid "
"Statistieken en of je notificaties wilt krijgen van updates die in het "
"systeem plaats vinden."

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:100
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid "Duplicate Contact page"
msgstr "dubbele contacten"

#: dt-assets/parts/modals/modal-help.php:101
msgctxt "Optional Documentation"
msgid ""
"This Duplicate Contact Page is where you can review, decline or merge "
"contacts that have been picked up by the system (checking against their "
"name, email and phone) as possibly being duplicates of another already "
"existing contact."
msgstr ""
"Deze Duplicaat contact pagina is waar je kunt nagaan, weigeren of contacten "
"kunt samenvoegen die door het systeem herkend zijn (controle op naam, e-mail "
"en telefoon) als mogelijke duplicaten van een bestaand contact."

